In order to see the assembly of loop.c:

clang -O0 -emit-llvm -c loop.c
opt -mem2reg loop.bc -o loop-m2r.bc
llvm-dis loop-m2r.bc
cat loop-m2r.ll

To run the liveness and reaching-definition passes:

opt -load ./liveness.so -cd-liveness loop-m2r.bc -o out.bc
opt -load ./reaching-definitions.so -cd-reaching-definitions loop-m2r.bc -o out.bc
